TAG IMAGES<LF>
==========<LF>
It is possible to tag images by assign searchable values to them.<LF>
<LF>
1:<LF>
Select the tab TAG IMAGES.<LF>
<LF>
2:<LF>
Select a directory with images that shall be tagged in the tree structure to the left.<LF>
<LF>
3:<LF>
Tag an image by clicking any of the images in the loaded image overview which was loaded in step 2 above. Enter a comment of unrestricted length in the field with the headline COMMENT. It is also possible to assign an image a classification on a scale from 1 to 5. Besides from this it is also possible to assign an unlimited amount of categories to an image.